<br>
Seriously, next step is laterns.  These will take you to 68.  Well, you can make cookie cutters to get you from 51-56 first - might be more entertaining. Also takes fewer items per combine (metal bits, mold, water for cookie cutters compared to metal bits, mold, bottle and water for lantern).<br>
<br>
After that, though, the cheapest route is the long and dreadful slog through skewers..... from 68 on up to 115.  You can try making weapons that trival earlier, but it's a) more expensive and b) uses more items per combine.<br>
<br>
